{"word":"εὐδοκέω","slug":"εὐδοκέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>εὐδοϰέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὖ\">εὖ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δοκέω\">δοκέω</a></el>; ‘be well pleased’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘consider beneficial and therefore worthy of choice’, <b>decide, resolve <a href='B:490 12:32'>Lk 12:32</a>; <a href='B:520 15:26'>Ro 15:26f</a>; <a href='B:530 1:21'>1 Cor 1:21</a>; <a href='B:540 5:8'>2 Cor 5:8</a>; <a href='B:550 1:15'>Gal 1:15</a>; <a href='B:580 1:19'>Col 1:19</a>; <a href='B:590 2:8'>1 Th 2:8</a>; <a href='B:590 3:1'>3:1</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘take delight’ in/with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>/someone, <b>be delighted, be well pleased <a href='B:470 3:17'>Mt 3:17</a>; <a href='B:540 12:10'>2 Cor 12:10</a>; <a href='B:600 2:12'>2 Th 2:12</a>; <a href='B:680 1:17'>2 Pt 1:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐδία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐδοκία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}